  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  THA within 48 hours and VAS&gt;40 during active 30 degrees hip flexion despite
             conventional pain medication.

          -  informed consent

          -  ASA 1-3

          -  BMI 18-40

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Unable to communicate in danish

          -  Allergic reactions toward drugs used

          -  Abuse of alcohol/drugs

          -  Unable to cooperate

          -  Pregnant women
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
